snippet.title: Against the Wall - Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Against the Wall is a video game that is currently in development. In it, players journey up the side of an infinite wall, encountering civilizations, creatures, machines, and puzzles along the way.

You can play the alpha version of the game at http://www.againstthewallgame.com/play/

You can pre-order the game through PayPal at: http://www.againstthewallgame.com/store/

Edited by Jennifer Joelle Kachler with music by Zoe Blade.
